wardenips (0.3.0~beta1-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add robust timestamp-based relative time rendering across dashboards
  * Add country enrichment fallback and improve geo heatmap mapping behavior
  * Enrich ban/report notifications with honeypot-aware explanations
